snippet.title: Blocky Ascent: Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2682470/Blocky_Ascent/

Each step matters in this high-stakes first-person parkour platformer, as falling means losing progress. Overcome dynamic obstacles like moving platforms and anti-gravity fields. Discover shortcuts to reach the summit faster, but beware, the climb demands mastery. Will you conquer the ascent?
